{"tid":2451643,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"奴工處籲資方彈性安排放清明節及復活節長假 免集中掃墓播疫","createTime":"2021-03-18T09:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T00:19:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb1ad55b78c1f45db5c0236ce2ff13b9cffeec1","tid":2451643,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"勞工處籲僱主彈性安排放清明節假 免集中掃墓播疫<br />\n<br />\n勞工處呼籲僱主彈性安排僱員放清明節假，以便僱員在假期前後的日子掃墓，避免人流聚集造成疫情傳播。今年清明節假期在4月4日，亦是復活節假期期間，法例定明僱主可預先通知僱員，在假期前後60日內，為僱員另外安排日子放假。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383576&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2er6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=5c3e7af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383576</a>"},{"pid":"7dd1f6385db46978771b813447ecbd2f0f319ac2","tid":2451643,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfd5da7339ff9499db5287c860d57e75b6d647e","tid":2451643,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"收到<br />\n尊重傳統應該清明正日拜山嘅"},{"pid":"77e0fbdab61abe893915f69f601a2582506aa1a0","tid":2451643,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:09:02.000Z","msg":"打風呼籲公司體諒員工遲到<br />\n交通問題呼籲僱主體諒員工<br />\n疫情呼籲公司安排wfh<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad3dccfe60c45f2d36261ca3c8b749f79399f34","tid":2451643,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:19:56.000Z","msg":"wfh未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}